# Package manager: Bun

Treat **Bun** as this repo’s main package manager. Prefer Bun in agent shell commands, docs, and CI snippets unless the user explicitly asks for another tool or you are debugging a manager-specific issue.

## Commands

| Task                       | Use                                                       |
| -------------------------- | --------------------------------------------------------- |
| Install deps               | `bun install`                                             |
| Add / remove / update      | `bun add …`, `bun remove …`, `bun update …`               |
| Run `package.json` scripts | `bun run <script>` (e.g. `bun run lint`, `bun run start`) |
| One-off binaries           | `bunx <pkg>` instead of `npx`                             |

## Do not

- Default to `npm`, `pnpm`, or `yarn` for routine installs or script runs in this project.
- Add alternate lockfiles (`package-lock.json`, `pnpm-lock.yaml`, `yarn.lock`) unless the user requires them.

## Lockfile

Keep the Bun lockfile (`bun.lock` / `bun.lockb`, whichever the project uses) in sync with dependency changes and commit it with those changes when applicable.
